  "prompt": "What percentage of questions are yet to be answered in Quora?",
  "response": "As of my last update, Quora has not publicly disclosed the exact number of unanswered questions on their platform. The total number of questions and the percentage that remain unanswered can fluctuate daily due to new questions being asked and existing ones being answered.\n\nHowever, you can find the latest statistics and possibly an estimate by visiting Quora's official statistics page or by checking reports from third-party analytics services that track such data. Keep in mind that the figure can vary, and only Quora's internal data would provide the exact current percentage of unanswered questions.",
